<!-- FEATURE IMAGES -->
<section class="feature-full" style="min-height:85vh"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2025/06/09/都市之美 拷贝_20240719170802A049_20250609143947A132.jpg" alt="EU5 PLUS"><div class="feature-overlay"><h3 data-i18n="eu5plus.urbanElectricElegance">Urban Electric Elegance</h3><p data-i18n="eu5plus.urbanElectricEleganceDesc">R500 with 416km NEDC range or R600 with 501km range. 120kW permanent magnet synchronous motor with 240N&middot;m torque. Fast charge 30%-80% in &le;30 minutes. Maximum speed 150km/h.</p></div></section>

<section><div class="feature-side"><div class="feature-side-img"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2025/06/09/轴距 拷贝_20240719170815A050_20250609144030A135.jpg" alt="Wheelbase"></div><div class="feature-side-content"><h3 data-i18n="eu5plus.generousDimensions">Generous Dimensions</h3><p data-i18n="eu5plus.generousDimensionsDesc">4670&times;1820&times;1520mm with 2670mm wheelbase. 12.3-inch LCD instrument and 12.3-inch center screen. Leather steering wheel with multi-function controls. Automatic anti-glare rearview mirror on Honor/R600.</p></div></div></section>

<section class="feature-full" style="min-height:80vh"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2025/06/09/灯光_20240719170916A054_20250609144057A138.jpg" alt="Lighting"><div class="feature-overlay"><h3 data-i18n="eu5plus.fullLedLighting">Full LED Lighting</h3><p data-i18n="eu5plus.fullLedLightingDesc">LED front and rear lights standard across all trims. Automatic headlights with follow-me-home function. LED daytime running lights, emergency stop signal, and ambient lighting on Honor/R600.</p></div></section>

<section><div class="feature-duo"><div class="feature-duo-item"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2024/07/19/内饰_20240719170943A058.jpg" alt="Interior"><div class="feature-duo-ov"><h4 data-i18n="eu5plus.premiumInterior">Premium Interior</h4><p data-i18n="eu5plus.premiumInteriorDesc">Micro-fiber sports seats, 6-way electric driver seat, wireless charging on Honor</p></div></div><div class="feature-duo-item"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2025/06/09/钢架_20240719171039A060_20250609144149A142.jpg" alt="Safety"><div class="feature-duo-ov"><h4 data-i18n="eu5plus.rigidBodyStructure">Rigid Body Structure</h4><p data-i18n="eu5plus.rigidBodyStructureDesc">ESP+TCS, ABS+EBD, HHC, HDC, Auto Hold, ISOFIX, DVR standard</p></div></div></div></section>

<section><div class="feature-side" style="direction:rtl"><div class="feature-side-img" style="direction:ltr"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2025/06/09/操控 拷贝_20240719171105A062_20250609144224A144.jpg" alt="Handling"></div><div class="feature-side-content" style="direction:ltr"><h3 data-i18n="eu5plus.advancedAdas">Advanced ADAS</h3><p data-i18n="eu5plus.advancedAdasDesc">Honor and R600 feature AEB with vehicle and pedestrian detection, ACC adaptive cruise, FCW/PCW collision warnings, BSD blind spot detection, LDW lane departure, and AVM surround view. R600 adds V2L/V2V capability.</p></div></div></section>

<section><div class="feature-duo"><div class="feature-duo-item"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2025/06/09/充电 拷贝_20240719171135A067_20250609144302A149.jpg" alt="Charging"><div class="feature-duo-ov"><h4 data-i18n="eu5plus.dualChargingOptions">Dual Charging Options</h4><p data-i18n="eu5plus.dualChargingOptionsDesc">Fast charge &le;0.5h (30-80%), general charge &le;8.5h (R500) / &le;10h (R600)</p></div></div><div class="feature-duo-item"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2025/06/09/电控en_20250609161929A203.jpg" alt="Battery"><div class="feature-duo-ov"><h4 data-i18n="eu5plus.intelligentBatteryManagement">Intelligent Battery Management</h4><p data-i18n="eu5plus.intelligentBatteryManagementDesc">Ternary lithium battery with intelligent temperature control system</p></div></div></div></section>

